source.name: Yellow Medallion Taxicabs - Agents
source.description:
Yellow Medallion Taxicabs are the official taxis of New York City. There are currently about 13,000 licensed taxicabs and they provide transportation for passengers via street hails.

This list includes Medallion Agent Licensee names, license numbers, addresses, and phone numbers.
